Those with net assets before financing amounting to not more than P100,000.00....P1,000.00 per annum;

Those with net assets before financing of more than P100,000.00 to P250,000.00....P2,500.00 per annum;

Those with net assets before financing of more than P250,000.00 to P400,000.00....P4,000.00 per annum; and

Those with net assets before financing of more than P400,000.00 to P500,000.00....P5,000.00 per annum.

In the event the CBBE uses a brand name on its products, such brand name shall first be registered with the Bureau of Domestic Trade, through the Department of Trade and Industry (DTI) provincial office.
